data.description: DON'T WAIT, INTEREST RATES ARE DROPPING. Enjoy peace and quiet in this stunning single story home. Spacious open floorplan is perfect for entertaining, allowing you to create unforgettable memories with family and friends right from the moment you move in. Prepare incredible feasts in the kitchen, equipped with quartz countertops, tile backsplash, high quality appliances, beautiful cabinetry, and an island perfect for breakfast time. HUGE PANTRY too! Luxurious owners suite with a great bathroom & large walk in closet.  Bonus room perfect for a home office or play area.  Built solid in 2017, before Covid when the shortage of workers and quality of the materials and craftsmanship was not a problem.This home has a better floor plan than the competition, offering you peace of mind and confidence in your home. Get more value for your hard-earned dollar. No need to wait, move-in ready. Take a tour today!
